                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Before the hardlight havoc begins its turn in combat, it gains one of the following error states at random, losing any previous error state.</p>\n<p><strong>Change Character</strong> The hardlight havoc regains @Damage[2d8[healing]|options:area-damage] Hit Points.</p>\n<p><strong>Pixelation</strong> The hardlight havoc is @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Concealed] from all creatures.</p>\n<p><strong>Power Leak</strong> The hardlight havoc is @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Stunned]{Stunned 1}. At the end of its turn, it deals @Damage[4d6[electricity]|options:area-damage] damage to creatures in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:10] (@Check[reflex|dc:22|basic] save).</p>\n<p><strong>Surge</strong> The hardlight havoc is @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Quickened] until the end of its turn and can use the extra action to Stride or Strike.</p>"
                },
